transcript.text: Hi! I am cobbling together a short notice inspiration trip.
Could you please share your preferred destination and travel dates for this trip? If you have any specific preferences, such as a preferred time of day for departure or arrival, let me know!

Great choice! How many passengers will be traveling, and do you have any other preferences for the flight, such as a specific time of day or class preference?
Please keep the origin flexible: use my nearest airport if helpful, otherwise anything within 100km of my current spot in Zaprešić.
Thank you for the details! Now, could you please specify the number of passengers and any other preferences you might have, such as a specific time of day or class preference?
